Package: rollply
Title: Moving-Window Add-on for Plyr
Version: 0.4
Author: "Alexandre Genin <alex@lecairn.org> [aut, cre]"
Maintainer: Alexandre Genin <alex@lecairn.org>
Description: Apply a function in a moving window, then
             combine the results in a data frame.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
Imports:
    plyr,
    Rcpp,
    scales,
    stringr
License: GPL (>=2)
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: testthat,
          knitr,
          proj4,
          ggplot2,
          rgdal,
          tidyr,
          alphahull
URL: http://alex.lecairn.org/rollply.html, https://github.com/alexgenin/rollply
BugReports: https://github.com/alexgenin/rollply
